Package: optbinningR
Type: Package
Title: Optimal Binning for Credit Scoring and Risk Modeling
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(given = "Sahaj", family = "Team", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "maintainer@example.com")
    )
Description: An R interface for optimal binning workflows inspired by the Python
    optbinning package. It provides native R APIs for binary, multiclass and
    continuous optimal binning, including BinningProcess and a binary Scorecard
    workflow.
